oad</h2><p>Tally report data is not automatically uploaded to Samriddhi Associates. Files or screenshots are received only when the user voluntarily shares them for support.</p></div><div class="policy"><h2>Licence validation</h2><p>Licence Key, registered contact details, installation or device identifier, licence status and validation timestamps may be transmitted securely to the Samriddhi Associates licence service. Tally report contents are not required for licence validation.</p></div><div class="policy"><h2>Storage and retention</h2><p>Local reports, settings and temporary records remain under the user’s control and can be deleted through the application or operating system where available. Licence records may be retained for activation, support, fraud prevention and administration.</p></div><div class="policy"><h2>Sharing and sale</h2><p>Samriddhi Associates does not sell Tally or report data. Data may be disclosed only when required by law or when voluntarily supplied by the user for support.</p></div><div class="policy"><h2>User responsibility</h2><p>The user must protect local accounting data, select the correct company and period, and verify all generated reports before using them for accounting, tax, audit or business decisions.</p></div><div class="policy"><h2>Contact</h2><p>Samriddhi Associates<br/>+91-98299-27177</p></div></div></section><footer class="site-footer"><div class="footer-grid"><div><h3>Samriddhi Associates</h3><p>Practical software tools for GST professionals, businesses and authorised users.</p><p><strong>Contact:</strong><br/><strong>Samriddhi Associates</strong><br/>8, Basement Floor, Okay Plus Complex, Near Bus Stand, Kishangarh, Ajmer - 305801<br/>Cell : +91-98299-27177</p></div><div><h3>Products</h3><a href="../gst-tool/index.html">GST & E-Way Login Tool</a><a href="../gmail-sender/index.html">Samriddhi Gmail Sender</a><a href="../gst-return-downloader/index.html">GST Return Downloader</a><a href="../gstr-2b-reconciliation/index.htm